6 months. He never visited nor paid for medication for my child. ”He has failed as a husband,” she said. [NAN] Vanguard News Nigeria One Mrs. Morufat Rabiu, dragged to the court by husband, Mr. Oladipupo Rabiu, was accused of always stealing and engaging in fight with co-tenants and himself. September 5, 2015 In "News" Lagos—The presiding President of a Lagos Customary Court sitting at Agboyi/Ketu, Mr. O. T. Williams, yesterday advised women to always do proper investigation before going into marriage. November 10, 2015 In "News" Lagos, that her husband, Onu, deceived her and her parents and paid just N600 as her bride price when she was still 12 years old. She also said that sometimes he strips her naked and beats her to pulp. September 8, 2016 In "News"